          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Coronavirus Help And Response Initiative Through Year 2022 Act or the CHARITY 2022 Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows a taxpayer a deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for charitable contributions for a taxable year beginning in 2020-2022, even if such taxpayer does not otherwise itemize deductions. The deduction may not exceed one-third of the taxpayer's standard deduction amount.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-04-10T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
